inputs.text:
A breathtaking masterpiece anime illustration in the style of Kyoto Animation and Ufotable. A mesmerizing young sorceress floating gently above a reflective wet rooftop in a futuristic cyberpunk city at night.
Character details: She has waist-length iridescent silver hair that glows faintly in the dark, and expressive heterochromia eyes (one sapphire blue, one golden). She is wearing an intricate gothic lolita dress modified with translucent holographic fabrics and mechanical accessories.
Atmosphere & Action: She is casting a spell, holding a glowing magic orb made of glass and starlight. Swirling blue magic particles and fireflies surround her.
Environment: The background features towering neon skyscrapers blurred by rain and depth of field. The ground is wet and reflects the neon lights and the character perfectly.
Technical qualities: Cinematic lighting, volumetric fog, Tyndall effect, bloom, sharp focus on the face, highly detailed digital art, 8k resolution, vibrant colors, ray tracing.
